description: Noncomposites together with such composites n = p_i * p_j * p_k * ... * p_u, p_i <= p_j <= p_k <= ... <= p_u, where there is at least one such pair of successive prime factors (when sorted into a nondecreasing order) that the square of the former is larger than the latter: (p_i)^2 > p_j or (p_j)^2 > p_k, etc.
